text: Mame Madior Boye (born 1940"Mame Madior Boye", Jeune Afrique, August 13, 2007 .) is a Senegalese politician. He was Prime Minister of Senegal from 2001 to 2002. She was the first female holder of that position. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Senegal
